<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>coldkey — Age Post-Quantum Key Backup</title>
<style>
  @page { size: letter; margin: 0.4in 0.5in; }
  @media print { .no-print { display: none; } }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    max-width: 7.5in;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0;
    color: #111;
    font-size: 9pt;
  }
  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    color: #b91c1c;
    font-size: 1.3em;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #b91c1c;
    padding-bottom: 0.2em;
    margin: 0 0 0.2em;
  }
  table.meta {
    margin: 0 auto 0.4em;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: #333;
  }
  table.meta td { padding: 0.05em 0.5em; }
  table.meta td:first-child { font-weight: bold; text-align: right; color: #555; }
  table.meta td:last-child { font-family: "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 0.92em; }
  .section-label {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    margin: 0.5em 0 0.15em;
    color: #333;
  }
  .key-block {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.4em 0.6em;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-all;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .columns {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.6em;
    margin-top: 0.4em;
  }
  .col-qr { flex: 0 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .col-qr svg { width: 2.4in; height: 2.4in; }
  .col-right { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .qr-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4em;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 0.4em;
  }
  .qr-cell { text-align: center; }
  .qr-cell svg { width: 2.2in; height: 2.2in; }
  .qr-label {
    font-size: 0.8em;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 0.1em;
  }
  .qr-meta {
    font-size: 0.75em;
    color: #666;
    margin-top: 0.1em;
  }
  .checksum {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.3em 0.5em;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 8pt;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .recovery {
    font-size: 0.82em;
    margin-top: 0.5em;
    color: #333;
  }
  .recovery ol { margin: 0.2em 0; padding-left: 1.5em; }
  .recovery li { margin-bottom: 0.1em; }
  .warning {
    color: #b91c1c;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.75em;
    color: #999;
    margin-top: 0.4em;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Age Post-Quantum Private Key &mdash; DO NOT SHARE</h1>

<table class="meta">
  <tr><td>Generated</td><td>{{.Date}}</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="section-label">Raw Key File</div>
<div class="key-block">{{.RawKeyContent}}</div>

{{if eq .TotalQRParts 1}}
<div class="columns">
  <div class="col-qr">
    <div class="section-label">QR Code (private key only)</div>
    {{(index .QRChunks 0).SVG}}
    <div class="qr-meta">{{(index .QRChunks 0).DataLen}} / {{.MaxQRCapacity}} bytes ({{.QRUsagePct}}%)</div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-right">
    <div class="section-label">SHA-256 Checksum</div>
    <div class="checksum">{{.SHA256}}</div>
    <div class="recovery">
      <strong>Recovery</strong>
      <ol>
        <li>Scan QR code to recover the private key, or type it from the raw key text above</li>
        <li>Regenerate the public key: <code>age-keygen -y</code> with the private key</li>
        <li>Reconstruct the key file and save to <code>~/.config/sops/age/keys.txt</code></li>
        <li>Verify: <code>sha256sum keys.txt</code> matches checksum</li>
        <li>Test: <code>sops -d &lt;any .sops file&gt;</code></li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="warning" style="margin-top:0.6em;">
      This key decrypts all SOPS secrets. Store securely. Shred digital copies after printing.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{{else}}
<div class="section-label">QR Codes ({{.TotalQRParts}} parts)</div>
<div class="qr-grid">
  {{range .QRChunks}}
  <div class="qr-cell">
    <div class="qr-label">Part {{.Part}} of {{.Total}}</div>
    {{.SVG}}
    <div class="qr-meta">{{.DataLen}} bytes</div>
  </div>
  {{end}}
</div>

<div class="section-label">SHA-256 Checksum</div>
<div class="checksum">{{.SHA256}}</div>

<div class="recovery">
  <strong>Recovery (multi-QR)</strong>
  <ol>
    <li>Scan all {{.TotalQRParts}} QR codes in order to recover the private key</li>
    <li>Strip the <code>COLDKEY:N/M:</code> prefix from each payload</li>
    <li>Concatenate payloads to reconstruct the private key</li>
    <li>Regenerate the public key: <code>age-keygen -y</code> with the private key</li>
    <li>Reconstruct the key file and save to <code>~/.config/sops/age/keys.txt</code></li>
    <li>Verify: <code>sha256sum keys.txt</code> = <code>{{.SHA256}}</code></li>
  </ol>
</div>
<div class="warning" style="margin-top:0.4em;">
  This key decrypts all SOPS secrets. Store securely. Shred digital copies after printing.
</div>
{{end}}

<p class="no-print" style="text-align:center; margin-top:1em;">
  <button onclick="window.print()" style="padding:0.4em 1.5em; font-size:1em; cursor:pointer;">Print</button>
</p>

<div class="footer">Generated by coldkey {{.Version}}</div>

</body>
</html>
